import React from 'react'
import Header from '../HomePage/Header'
import Footer from '../HomePage/Footer'
import ContainerFAQs from './ContainerFAQs'
import './FAQs.css'

function FAQs() {
  return (
    <>
        <Header/>
        <ContainerFAQs/>
        <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default FAQs
